					<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

					<p>Welcome to www.investedok.org (the “Site”). The Site is operated by the Oklahoma Department of Securities (Department). This Privacy Policy explains what the Department does with data collected as a result of your visit to or use of this Site, including personally identifiable information (Personal Information).  Personal Information includes names, addresses, phone numbers, and other information that is readily identifiable to a specific individual.   The Department reserves the right to change this policy at any time and you should occasionally review it to monitor any changes.</p>
					<h5>Data Collection and Use</h5>
					<h6>Information collected when you browse the Site</h6>
					<p>The Department has designed the Site so that you are not required to provide any Personal Information unless you access certain functions on the Site.  When you merely browse this Site, the Department has access to, but does not generally retain, the information collected by Google Analytics.  The Department reviews the Google Analytics information to improve the content of its web services and to understand how people are using such services.  To learn how the information collected is used by Google, please go to <a href="https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/">https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/partners/</a>.</p>
					<h6>Information collected if you volunteer information</h6>
					<p>If during your visit to the Site you participate in a survey, send the Department an email, participate in the Students Tracking and Researching the Stock Market program (STARS program), or perform some other transaction online, the following Personal Information may be collected:</p>
